flowRoot.flowPara: -This community is for Ingress, not for Pokémon GO. While a certain amount of subjectiveness is applied to memes and artwork, posts deemed off-topic will be removed.﻿
-The same image re-shared in rapid succession, or spamming the community in general, will result in a removal of the post(s) and a potential ban from the community.

-Posting inappropriate and offensive content that includes but is not limited to sexual or pornographic content, obscenity, or hate speech will result in the removal of the post and a potential ban from the community. We want Ingress to be a fun and safe experience for all players, and for everyone out in the real world and within our online community.﻿
